Description: NWS weather alerts for AllStar/Asterisk nodes
 CAP-Alert fetches National Weather Service alerts (and optional NHC
 cyclone advisories), builds audio from bundled ulaw sound files and
 TTS, and plays them on a configured AllStar node.
 .
 On install, an interactive setup wizard collects node number, location,
 and optional features (cyclone tracking, Pushover, CPU temperature alarms).
 Scheduled polling uses a systemd timer (cap-alert.timer).
